cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DL, cs.SE, cs.DB

The paper discusses the institutional approach for organizing and maintaining ontologies, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of category theory and indexed categories also suggests a connection to deep learning (cs.DL). The Information Flow Framework, which is mentioned in the paper, involves semantic integration and maintenance of ontologies, which are topics related to software engineering (cs.SE) and databases (cs.DB).
